episodes.description:
When Christian influencer couple Paul and Morgan share personal health struggles, they unintentionally reveal a deeper, troubling issue—how evangelical culture often dismisses or mishandles medical needs. In this exvangelical deep dive, we examine their story as a case study on how faith communities can contribute to medical neglect, the harmful narratives that keep believers from seeking proper care, and why this pattern is so pervasive in church spaces.

